content:
My almost 3 year old loves Starfall numbers. I am so glad that I downloaded 
this app for her. She's really engaged and learning at the same time. I 
absolutely love that this doesn't need an internet connection.
I have bought numerous learning apps and by starfall is the best!!
All of them crash and freeze up except for the ABC app. I paid for these apps and my little ones havent even been able to use them because they freeze and crash while they are using them
